      • setConfirmVM

        public void setConfirmVM(Manager manager,
                         VM prev,
                         VM next,
                         int x,
                         int y)
        Method sets the requisite options for Confirmation.
        Parameters:
        manager - The active Manager to which the outcome of the confirmation will apply.
        prev - The viewmode to be returned to if the confirmation is negative.
        next - The viewmode to be advanced to if the confirmation is positive.
        x - The x coordinate of the top-left point of the confirmation box.
        y - The y corrdinate of the top-left point of the confirmation box.
